# Platform API docs (generated)
.platform-api-docs/

# Agent skills
# Copy `.skills.local.example` to `.skills.local` and edit `SKILLS_DOMAINS=`.
.skills.local

# Public MetaMask/skills cache maintained by `yarn skills` / `yarn setup`.
.skills-cache/

